sorry to bother you.</i>

9
00:01:26,380 --> 00:01:28,079
<i>Can I help you?</i>

10
00:01:32,300 --> 00:01:33,779
Sir, take our picture!

11
00:01:33,780 --> 00:01:36,099
<i>Is that a children's movie, Sir?</i>

12
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:39,539
<i>Mr. Safavi, take a picture
of these children.</i>

13
00:01:39,580 --> 00:01:41,979
