<i>Lion-hearted one?
- Is Ali.</i>

64
00:06:03,539 --> 00:06:05,819
<i>Conqueros of Kheibar?
- Is Ali.</i>

65
00:06:05,820 --> 00:06:09,099
<i>The first Imam?
- Is Ali.</i>

66
